}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== FCC ID 2ABZMW63AP is a change in ID request from V7TI24 of the [[Tenda i24]]. [[Qualcomm]] CPU and radio chip IDs are not shown in the FCC internal photos. The CPU is assumed to be a QCA9531 like what's in the [[Tenda W15E V2]]. WI2 is likely a QCA9886 since it is 2x2 and supports MU-MIMO.
"10038683" and "V1.0" are silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
